      <title>Discover Your Patterns of Wisdom</title>
      <description>Anthony Lawlor, internationally known architect and author, joins me this week for the ultimate discussion – recognizing and using our patterns of wisdom. Consciousness, from a human perspective, is a magical weaving of thought patterns, behavior patterns, and emotional response patterns, and for every human being there are reservoirs of unique wisdom encoded in those patterns. Yet it’s hard for us to recognize this because we’ve trained our awareness to focus on the material world, and the patterns themselves, though precise, are intangible. We need a tool set that includes a tangible reference point in order to transit from the limited world of form to the limitless world of consciousness, vision, and innovative possibility. Anthony brings us that tool set in his latest book, The 24 Patterns of Wisdom: Navigating the Challenges and Awakenings of the Human Journey. In an inspired use of symbol, he shows us how patterns of energy and intelligence shape our human experience. Join us!</description>
