      <description>This week Dr. Bob Uslander, founder of www.DoctorsOnPurpose.com, joins me for a practical discussion of purpose, passion, and meaningful service as key ingredients for a fulfilled and joyful life. No doubt we have a plethora of books and seminars – all telling us how to find our calling and achieve happiness as individuals – but very few recognize a key link that makes Bob Uslander’s work unique. His understanding of the relationship between the individual and the collective and his insistence that any solution devised for one must work for the other are the ingredients that bring his work into the arena of consciousness and generate awakened value and success for his clients. In addition to being an experienced MD, he is a natural problem-solver and an entrepreneur – he knows how to deliver ‘prescriptions’ for living well, in joy, personally and professionally. Whether you’re in the health professions or another field, learn how to find your path of celebration and live on purpose.</description>
