      <title>Abundance: A Way of Being</title>
      <description>Jerry Michalski, founder of the REXpedition, joins me to dissolve old beliefs and unfold exciting new perspectives on abundance and how it’s actually created and sustained. In modern cultures we still tend to link abundance to doing the right thing so we’ll have enough to be safe and secure. We’ve woven money and material goods so tightly into our idea of abundance that we can barely separate them. Yet the ‘if I do this then I’ll have that’ approach is purely linear; in fact it’s the only approach we can perceive in linear awareness. It leaves us no alternatives; it doesn’t connect us to support networks or new economies. It’s only in full consciousness that the core organizing principles bring us into dimensional relationship networks whose soul purpose is to create and evolve abundance. Discover what this looks like in business and in life; learn what it is to source from being rather than doing. And tune in to discover the power of the REXpedition and your ability to BE abundant!</description>
